{
  "uuid": "ed2e96aedcc4a70bba9e9271a6da0933",
  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Assistant ENGINEER ( CIVIL) cum Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>A. Main\nResponsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>1. Technical\nDrafting & Design (Primary Focus)</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare detailed technical drawings using <strong>AutoCAD</strong>;\n     knowledge of <strong>BIM</strong> is a must.</li><li>Perform drafting, design work, and\n     structural/civil engineering calculations.</li><li>Ensure drawings and designs comply with\n     company standards, client requirements, and regulatory guidelines.</li><li>Maintain proper documentation control and\n     filing systems for all technical drawings and design documents.</li><li>Collaborate with Project Manager,\n     Engineer, and Quantity Surveyor to ensure accurate representation of\n     design in drawings.</li></ul><p><strong>2. Site Supervision\n& Compliance</strong></p><ul><li>Support supervisors, foremen, and workers\n     to ensure on-site activities follow approved drawings and regulatory\n     requirements.</li><li>Conduct occasional site inspections to\n     verify implementation of technical plans.</li></ul><p><strong>3. Site\nAdministration (Secondary Focus)</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in office administration tasks at\n     the site office, including documentation, data entry, purchase orders\n     (issue material requisition to purchaser), deliveries, goods receipt,\n     machinery, and manpower coordination.</li><li>Coordinate meetings and assist Project\n     Manager in daily administrative tasks.</li></ul><p><strong>4. Progress\nReporting & Claims (Secondary Focus)</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in preparing monthly progress\n     claims and reports, especially related to technical deliverables and\n     drawings.</li></ul><p><strong>5. Project\nExecution & Quality Control</strong></p><ul><li>Support engineers in reviewing and\n     verifying work to meet contractual and quality standards.</li><li>Assist in monitoring construction progress\n     against design specifications.</li></ul><p><strong>6. Environmental,\nSafety, and Health Compliance</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure Environmental, Safety, and Health\n     practices are adhered to at all times.</li></ul><p><strong>7. Ad-hoc Duties</strong></p><ul><li>Perform other duties as assigned from time\n     to time.</li></ul><p><strong>B. Safety\nResponsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate commitment to Occupational\n     Health & Safety (OHS) requirements.</li></ul><p><strong>C. Environmental\nResponsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Demonstrate commitment to Environmental\n     Management System (EMS) requirements.</li></ul>",
